m/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.103bnvdrwuun-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.103bnvdrwuun-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>可以购买的时尚单​​品包括<strong>外套、内衣、下装、袜子、鞋子和配饰</strong>，每件都可以单独购买。即使只是一件衣服也会给你的印象带来很大的不同。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.j2duypnc0wcg-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.j2duypnc0wcg-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.j2duypnc0wcg-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.j2duypnc0wcg-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.j2duypnc0wcg-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>您需要了解的一件事是，每种时尚单品都有自己的“库存”概念。当库存为0时，会显示“SOLDOUT”，您将无法再购买。<strong>当我本周初去时，有几件商品已经卖完了。</strong></p><p>按照官方的说法，库存会补货，不过以后的更新中似乎会增加“批号”，而且前期购买的物品都是有纪念意义的，所以你会想保住你想要的东西也是尽快的。</p><h2>改变你外表的“ALT BEAUTYS”</h2><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.ctudf0q1bjrd-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.ctudf0q1bjrd-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.ctudf0q1bjrd-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.ctudf0q1bjrd-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.ctudf0q1bjrd-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> “ALT BEAUTYS”是一家拥有时尚沙龙<strong>“ALT STYLE”</strong>和诊所<strong>“ALT CLINIC”</strong>的设施。它位于中央大楼后面稍远的地方。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.nqhjdko2sl1t-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.nqhjdko2sl1t-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.nqhjdko2sl1t-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.nqhjdko2sl1t-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.nqhjdko2sl1t-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.eparvllqsyoq-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.eparvllqsyoq-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.eparvllqsyoq-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.eparvllqsyoq-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.eparvllqsyoq-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>在造型沙龙里，你可以改变发型、脸部零件和妆容。每个区块（前/侧/后）的头发都可以改变，仅通过组合初始发型就可以显着改变印象。您还可以购买新发型并打造自己的发型。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.on9fjs7jjl21-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb0305bfe9-kix.on9fjs7jjl21-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/f0bb80da1233c8002bc991fb